data.description: Ask about Assumable 3.25% loan. Beautiful ranch style with a private brick fenced backyard featuring a covered patio. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious floor plan with a living room already wired for surround sound. Contemporary open concept features both dining space and seating at your kitchen island. This floor plan features a bonus room well suited for an office located at front of house with window view, far separated from bedrooms. Large primary on-suite features tile, dual sinks, separate tub and shower and plenty of storage space and walk in closet. Enjoy extra refreshing water with the whole house water filtration system. 5 minute drive from BNSF headquarters, quick access to I-35W and 820. Have Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity.
